<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="pile-vt">pile <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /paɪl/    美 /paɪl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>把……堆积；聚集：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please help us pile these books.
请帮我们把这些书摞好。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>piled</strong> his plate <strong>with</strong> as much food as he could.
他在盘子上盛了尽可能多的食物。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="pile-up">pile up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>堆积：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Work has piled up during his absence. 
在他离开期间，工作堆了一堆。</p></div></div>